        },
        {
            "title": "紫金礦業傳發行117億元可換股債  換股價溢價最少35%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">《彭博》報道，計劃發行5 年期零息可換股債券，集資15億美元(117億港元)，溢價較基準股價溢價35%至40%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"紫金黃金國際官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/601899-Web2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"紫金黃金國際官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/601899-Web2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">紫金黃金國際官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">紫金礦業今日收市價46.14元，最高見46.98元，創歷史新高。以今日收市價計，換股價約為62.29元至64.6元之間。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">報道指，債券集資用作秘魯La Arena項目資本支出。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15623022-%e7%b4%ab%e9%87%91%e7%a4%a6%e6%a5%ad%e5%82%b3%e7%99%bc%e8%a1%8c117%e5%84%84%e5%85%83%e5%8f%af%e6%8f%9b%e8%82%a1%e5%82%b5-%e6%ba%a2%e5%83%b9%e6%9c%80%e5%b0%9135",
