            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">在岸人民幣兌美元官方收6.9460，較上日官方收盤價跌7點，較上日夜盤收盤漲15點。</p>\n</div>",
