        {
            "title": "外電報稱紫金擬發換股債籌15億美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">《彭博》引述銷售文件指，紫金礦業(02899)擬發行可換股債券，向市場集資約15億美元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15622907-%e5%a4%96%e9%9b%bb%e5%a0%b1%e7%a8%b1%e7%b4%ab%e9%87%91%e6%93%ac%e7%99%bc%e6%8f%9b%e8%82%a1%e5%82%b5%e7%b1%8c15%e5%84%84%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/02899-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-29 16:37:50",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
